1350
01:25:34,487 --> 01:25:35,737
I don't get it.

1351
01:25:36,878 --> 01:25:38,878
Ben, Kim, are you there?

1352
01:25:39,950 --> 01:25:41,200
Do you hear me?

1353
01:25:42,133 --> 01:25:44,883
(dramatic music)

1354
01:25:48,600 --> 01:25:49,433
- Oh.

1355
01:25:54,874 --> 01:25:57,457
Oh man, that was one wild ride.

1356
01:26:02,968 --> 01:26:04,097
- Casey.

1357
01:26:04,097 --> 01:26:06,491
(screams)

1358
01:26:06,491 --> 01:26:10,158
- [Ghostly Voice] Go
ahead and do something.

1359
01:26:23,878 --> 01:26:26,517
- I guess we can thank M for that huh?

1360
01:26:26,517 --> 01:26:28,366
- I could've died.

1361
01:26:28,366 --> 01:26:30,866
