1372
01:26:51,707 --> 01:26:55,636
This little lady can take care of herself.

1373
01:26:55,636 --> 01:26:58,187
- Hey, it looks like we are
having pizza for dinner tonight.

1374
01:26:58,187 --> 01:26:59,937
- Yeah, pizza, pizza.

1375
01:27:01,747 --> 01:27:03,998
- [Narrator] Falco met
his match and was finally

1376
01:27:03,998 --> 01:27:06,554
defeated in the village down below.

1377
01:27:06,554 --> 01:27:10,110
As the legend goes his reign ended

1378
01:27:10,110 --> 01:27:12,817
when he was outwitted by a young boy

1379
01:27:12,817 --> 01:27:15,984
